<bibRefCitation author="Cockerell, T. D. A." box="[664,867,364,390]" pageId="7" pageNumber="485" pagination="394 - 403" refId="ref4212" refString="Cockerell, T. D. A. (1897 a) Contributions from the New Mexico Biological Station. - Some new Hymenoptera from the Mesilla Valley, New Mexico. The Annals and Magazine of Natural History, 19, 394 - 403. https: // doi. org / 10.1080 / 00222939708680555" type="journal article" year="1897">Cockerell (1897a)</bibRefCitation>
