<collectionCode box="[1026,1112,365,391]" country="USA" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/142r-0w94" name="Smithsonian Institution, National Museum of Natural History" pageId="7" pageNumber="485" type="Museum">NMNH</collectionCode>
being here designated as the 
<typeStatus box="[151,257,400,426]" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">lectotype</typeStatus>
. The specimen has the following data label (
<figureCitation box="[764,849,400,426]" captionStart="FIGURES 15–18" captionStartId="6.[151,270,1904,1928]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,797,1882]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[151,1436,797,1882]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="FIGURES 15–18. Centris cockerellii Fox, 1899 (lectotype female). Fig. 15: Frontal view. Fig. 16: Habitus, lateral view. Figs. 17 and 18: Labels. Fig. 17: Centris marginata Fox, 1899 (holotype male). Fig. 18: C. cockerellii (lectotype fe- male)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3430120" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3430120/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">Fig. 18</figureCitation>
): [whitish label] Las Cruces NM [printed]\ [whitish label] on 
<taxonomicName box="[257,489,436,462]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Caesalpinia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="7" pageNumber="485" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="falcaria">
<emphasis box="[257,489,436,462]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">Caesalpinia falcaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<date box="[496,590,436,463]" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">May 18.</date>
Ckll\ [whitish label] 
<taxonomicName box="[830,1028,436,463]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Caesalpinia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="7" pageNumber="485" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hoffmanseggia">
<emphasis box="[830,849,437,463]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">C</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[863,1028,436,462]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">hoffmanseggia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<specimenCount box="[1035,1056,437,463]" pageId="7" pageNumber="485" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
cotype. [handwritten]\ [red label] co [handwritten]-Type No. [printed] 3148 [handwritten] 
<collectingCountry box="[782,829,472,498]" name="United States of America" pageId="7" pageNumber="485">U.S.</collectingCountry>
N.M. [printed]\ [whitish label] Moure 1957 this specimen is the type of 
<taxonomicName authority="Fox" authorityName="Fox" authorityYear="1899" box="[365,618,508,535]" class="Insecta" family="Apidae" genus="Centris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="485" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cockerelli">
